s safety.</span></li><li style=\"display:flex;gap:16px;align-items:flex-start\"><i class=\"bi bi-check2-circle\" style=\"color:#10b981;font-size:1.25rem;margin-top:2px\"></i><span style=\"color:#334155;font-weight:500;line-height:1.5\">Anglers Park can get busy during mountain bike events—check the schedule if your dog is skittish.</span></li></ul></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"owner-cta\" class=\"owner-cta-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">Partner with us</span><h2>Feature your Danville dog park</h2><p>Upgrade to a featured listing, share live availability, or pitch a new indoor concept. Our team drives qualified local pet parents every week.</p><div class=\"hero-cta-row\" style=\"margin-top:24px\"><a class=\"hero-cta primary\" href=\"/list-your-park\">List a property</a><a class=\"hero-cta ghost\" href=\"/contact\">Contact the team</a></div></div></section><section id=\"park-directory\" class=\"park-directory-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><div class=\"section-heading\"><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">City directory</span><h2>All dog parks in <!-- -->Danville</h2><p>Filter-ready cards with ratings, amenities, and quick actions. Use the chips to jump between sections.</p></div><div class=\"category-chip-row\"><button type=\"button\">Dog Park</button></div><div id=\"dog-park-parks\" class=\"directory-category\"><div class=\"directory-header\"><div><h3>Dog Park<!-- -->s<!-- --> in <!-- -->Danville</h3><p>40<!-- --> locations ·<!-- --> <!-- -->4.4<!-- --> <!-- -->average rating</p></div><span class=\"directory-count\">40</span></div><div class=\"directory-grid\"><a class=\"park-card-premium-link\" href=\"/parks/abreu-grogan-park\"><div class=\"park-card-standard \"><div class=\"park-premium-header\"><h3 class=\"park-premium-title\">Abreu Grogan Park</h3><div class=\"park-header-group\"><div class=\"status-pill closed\">unknown</div><div class=\"park-premium-rating\"><i class=\"bi bi-star\"></i><span>5</span